Description: Contains a dataset of morphological and structural features of Medicibal LEAves ('MedLEA'). The features of each species is recorded by manually viewing the medicinal plant repository available at (<http://www.instituteofayurveda.org/plants/>). You can also download repository of leaf images of 1099 medicinal plants in Sri Lanka.
